## 🔴 ANTI-PATTERNS (PROVEN TO HURT)

| Technique | Avg LB Impact | Evidence |
|-----------|--------------|----------|
| Pseudo-labeling | **−0.003 to −0.005** | 3/3 attempts worse |
| Feature subspacing | **−0.004** | V4 scored 0.950 |
| Cleanlab denoising | **Fake OOF gain** | OOF 0.977, LB 0.953 |
| OOF > 0.960 | **Overfitting signal** | Every case confirmed |
| Differential Evolution weights | **−0.001** | Overfits to CV noise |

---

## 🟢 OOF CALIBRATION RULE

> **If OOF exceeds 0.960, STOP. You are overfitting.**

| OOF Range | LB Range | Diagnosis |
|-----------|----------|-----------|
| 0.955–0.957 | 0.953–0.954 | ✅ Optimal |
| 0.960–0.970 | 0.952–0.953 | ⚠️ Mild overfitting |
| 0.970+ | 0.950–0.953 | ❌ Severe overfitting |

